data.description: Income Producing Duplex in Jesup! Awesome investment opportunity that you don't want to miss out on! 1 unit is a 2/2 layout with large enclosed living room, dining area, and kitchen. Primary bedroom has attached private bathroom. The 2nd unit is 3/2 layout with separate living room and just off that is another large family room with built-ins and eat-in kitchen. Primary bedroom in this unit also has a private attached bathroom. Carport located on one side of the property as well as a storage shed out back. Large backyard with plenty of space! Being sold AS-IS.
